    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the interior is clean, showing only light wear on the driver's seat. On the exterior, you will find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use, but nothing that detracts from its overall solid appearance. It's a reliable choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that has been cared for.",
